# Git Conventions

## Commit Messages
```
type(scope): subject

body (optional)
```

Types: `feat`, `fix`, `docs`, `style`, `refactor`, `test`, `chore`

## Branch Naming
- `feature/[ticket]-[description]`
- `fix/[ticket]-[description]`
- `hotfix/[description]`
- `chore/[description]`

## Do NOT Commit
- Test/debug/investigate/temp/check/analyze scripts
- Images and output JSON files
- `.env` files or credentials
- Debug statements or commented-out code

## PR Requirements
- Descriptive title and description
- All tests passing
- No merge conflicts
- Reference issue numbers
